g ngy 17/10/2019 ti trng i Hc Thi Bnh Dng (08 Pasteur, Xng Hun, Thnh ph Nha Trang)  din ra chng trnh Nha Trang WordPress Meetup 10/2019 vi ch : <strong>TNG TC  LOAD WEBSITE WORDPRESS VI CACHE</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-845\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1-440x330.jpg 440w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/10/Nha-Trang-Meetup-10-2019-Pic-1.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-844\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Mc d tri ma rt to nhng vn c hn 20 bn n tham d meetup.<br><br>Ch : TNG TC  LOAD WEBSITE WORDPRESS VI CACHE c trnh by bi anh Minh Nguyn &#8211; CEO Minh Duy Solutions (Founder group Nha Trang WordPress). Vi cc k thut chnh gm: PHP Cache, Web Cache, Database Cache  gip cc bn tham d c ci nhn tng qut v u im ca vic s dng cache s tng tc  ca website v gip gim ti cho hosting, VPS ra sao, ng thi x l nhng nhc im c th gp trong qu trnh trin khai cache cho website WordPress.<br><br>Ban t chc meetup xin c gi li cm n chn thnh n Ban lnh o trng i hc Thi Bnh Dng  h tr rt nhiu trong vic cho mn phng hc  t chc meetup.<br><br>Ban t chc meetup cng xin gi li cm n n hai n v l 123host.vn v onedata.vn  ti tr nhng phn qu ht sc gi tr cho cng ng Nha Trang WordPress. Rt mong cc nh tri tr s lun ng hnh cng cng ng WordPress ni ring v cng ng ngun m ni chung.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xin mi cc bn cng xem mt s hnh nh ca bui meetup sng nay. Xin hn gp cc bn vo meetup ln sau.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block