w, 640px\" />											\n										<img width=\"640\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-840x840.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-840x840.jpg 840w, http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-365x365.jpg 365w, http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-768x768.jpg 768w, http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-300x300.jpg 300w, http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-600x600.jpg 600w, http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4-100x100.jpg 100w, http://cafey123.epizy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/19f9d0d8d160edef2190e8df3adb6ab4.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" />											\n		<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>II. NG GI</strong></h2><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 40px; color: #0c1325; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chun b nguyn vt liu: mn co</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cc bc thc hin:</p><p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000376681/file/5_d21f9833af734ef8b03012bbc7b85ebd_grande.png\" /></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bc 1: Dng mn co qun xung quanh khu vc thng.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bc 2: Dn tem ch dn hng d v v dn phiu giao nhn hng ln sn phm.</li></ul></li></ul><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; color: #0c1325; font-size: 28px;\">III. QUY NH V KCH THC V KHI LNG</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: #0c1325; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000376681/file/bang-gia-4__2__5adce09c8720422fb8f717b3b4493a1a.png\" /></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trng hp c s chnh lch gia khi lng thc t v khi lng quy i th GHN s p dng tnh cc i vi khi lng cao hn (Khi lng tnh cc). Khi lng quy i tnh theo cng thc:</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: #0c1325; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000376681/file/bang-gia-5__2__d081a9e1f71f49cf8b73f33b9d833231.png\" /></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trng hp Khi lng tnh cc b l s kg th s kg l (sau y tm gi l s X) s c lm trn ln nh sau:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 40px; color: #0c1325; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">X kg &lt; 0,5: s c lm trn l 0,5 kg</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">X kg &gt; 0,5 kg: s c lm trn l 1 kg.</li></ul><h2><strong>IV. QUY TRNH GI HNG</strong></h2><h3><strong>1. Ly hng - Nhn hng:</strong></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">GHN ch nhn hng  c ngi gi to trn h thng 5sao.ghn.vn hoc qua ng dng GHN, GHN c quyn t chi nhn n hng cha c to trn h thng.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi nhn hng, nhn vin giao nhn se  lai phiu nhn hng th hin nhng m vn on  nhn cho ngui gi  ngi gi khng bn giao hng nu nhn vin giao nhn khng cung cp phiu nhn hng v lin h tng i  GHN iu phi nhn vin giao nhn khc ly hng nhanh nht.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tt ca on hng tao truc 10h30 s c ly trc 12h00 cng ngy, to trc 16h00 s c ly trc 18h00 cng ngy.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">on hng phai uc ng gi, nhp khi lung v kch thuc thc theo quy inh. GHN c quyn t chi nu n hng khng c ng gi m bo hoc sai cn nng, khi lng.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong trung hp lin h khng thnh cng, nhn vin giao nhn se  lai tin nhn cho ngui gi.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mt m n hng tng ng mt kin hng.</li><li style=\"text-