px; color: #0c1325; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000376681/file/bang-gia-5__2__d081a9e1f71f49cf8b73f33b9d833231.png\" /></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trng hp Khi lng tnh cc b l s kg th s kg l (sau y tm gi l s X) s c lm trn ln nh sau:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 40px; color: #0c1325; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">X kg &lt; 0,5: s c lm trn l 0,5 kg</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">X kg &gt; 0,5 kg: s c lm trn l 1 kg.</li></ul><h2><strong>IV. QUY TRNH GI HNG</strong></h2><h3><strong>1. Ly hng - Nhn hng:</strong></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">GHN ch nhn hng  c ngi gi to trn h thng 5sao.ghn.vn hoc qua ng dng GHN, GHN c quyn t chi nhn n hng cha c to trn h thng.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi nhn hng, nhn vin giao nhn se  lai phiu nhn hng th hin nhng m vn on  nhn cho ngui gi  ngi gi khng bn giao hng nu nhn vin giao nhn khng cung cp phiu nhn hng v lin h tng i  GHN iu phi nhn vin giao nhn khc ly hng nhanh nht.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tt ca on hng tao truc 10h30 s c ly trc 12h00 cng ngy, to trc 16h00 s c ly trc 18h00 cng ngy.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">on hng phai uc ng gi, nhp khi lung v kch thuc thc theo quy inh. GHN c quyn t chi nu n hng khng c ng gi m bo hoc sai cn nng, khi lng.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong trung hp lin h khng thnh cng, nhn vin giao nhn se  lai tin nhn cho ngui gi.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mt m n hng tng ng mt kin hng.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">M on hng se uc huy trn h thng sau 3 ngy ly hng (bao gm ngy tao on hng) khng thnh cng vi l do n t ngui gi hng.</li></ul><h3><strong>2. Giao hng:</strong></h3><p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://file.hstatic.net/1000376681/file/bang-dich-vu-01_d8182066bff44fd38aeb323a9f394445.jpg\" /><