l; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\" srcset=\"https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-1.jpg 602w, https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-1-300x208.jpg 300w, https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-1-290x200.jpg 290w\" alt=\"sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-1\" width=\"602\" height=\"418\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1943\" /><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.5; color: #220e10; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; padding: 0px;\">Nhn bo dng, bo tr, hiu chnh my pha c ph chuyn nghip b li hoc xut hin sai s trong qu trnh s dng.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.8; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; margin-top: 5px !important; margin-bottom: 5px !important;\" src=\"https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\" srcset=\"https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2.jpg 602w, https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2-600x400.jpg 600w\" alt=\"sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-2\" width=\"602\" height=\"402\" /></p><ol style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cung cp cc loi bt lm sch nh : thuc v sinh my pha dng vin, dng bt, dng nc, dung dch descaling.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">V sinh h thng ni hi, ng ng, bm p sut my pha c ph.</li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">V sinh my pha c ph, v sinh li lc my pha, vi hi b kt, tc nc, thay th lc nc my pha c ph chuyn nghip.</li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.8; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; margin-top: 5px !important; margin-bottom: 5px !important;\" src=\"https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\" srcset=\"https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3.jpg 602w, https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://mayacacoffee.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3-600x400.jpg 600w\" alt=\"sua-chua-va-bao-tri-may-pha-ca-phe-3\" width=\"602\" height=\"402\" /><br />Nhn sa cha thay th bm p sut my pha c ph, bo mnh my pha c ph, ron my pha c ph cc dng my pha La cimbali ,Feama, Breville, Nouva Simonelli, Lelit, Casadio, Mellita, BFC, Royal, Iberital  khu vc min trung v ton quc.</p>", "DCH V", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "568-revision-v1", "", "", "2019-10-18 08:40:00", "2019-10-18 08:40:00", "", "568", "http://cafey123.epizy.com/2019/10/18/568-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
